form_2.itemText: This scale consistes of a number of words that describe different feelings and emotion. Read each item and then list the number from the scale below each word. Indicate (by clicking) to what extend you feel this way RIGHT NOW, that is, AT THE PRESENT MOMENT.
Press the + button to submit your answers
